[zero_shot][qwen2_5_0_5b_instruct][gsm8k] sample 61/100 done id=gsm8k_test_735 prediction="Let's solve this step-by-step:\n\n1. **Calculate Candidate A's Votes**:\n   - Candidate A got 20% of the votes.\n   - Number of votes for Candidate A = 20% of 100 voters = 0.20 * 100 = 20 votes.\n\n2. **Calculate Candidate B's Votes**:\n   - Candidate B got 50% more votes than Candidate A.\n   - Number of votes for Candidate B = 50% more than Candidate A’s votes.\n   - Number of votes for Candidate B = 20 + (0.50 * 20) = 20 + 10 = 30 votes.\n\n3. **Calculate Total Votes for Candidates A and B**:\n   - Total votes for Candidates A and B combined = 20 + 30 = 50 votes.\n\n4. **Calculate Candidate C's Votes**:\n   - Remaining votes for Candidate C = Total votes - Votes for Candidates A and B.\n   - Remaining votes for Candidate C = 100 - 50 = 50 votes.\n\nTherefore, Candidate C received 50 votes out of the total 100 voters." gold='50' correct=False
